From: Raju Rangoju <Raju.Rangoju@amd.com>
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:18:45 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 032/127] amd-xgbe: add support for new AN sequence

- Retains the original AN sequence
- Adds new AN sequence for Generations older than V3000 - untested
- Adds new AN sequence for V3000 - Sequence 2 (derived from krk2e)

Signed-off-by: Raju Rangoju <Raju.Rangoju@amd.com>
Change-Id: I9cb5924c54be7ca7f5cb95adde9e39e3bc879ab6
Signed-off-by: amlakshm <AmmuThivya.LakshmiS@amd.com>
